               breaking and entering the dwelling house of the <rs id="t17730113-53-viclabel315" type="occupation">Rev.</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17730113-53-victim593 t17730113-53-viclabel315"></join> 
                  
                     
